{"title":"山村的春节","authors":["侯龙柱"],"dates":[{"year":2002,"month":2,"day":14}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村的春节"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"侯龙柱"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春夜蹑手蹑脚"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从含苞欲放的花蕾中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"走下山坡悄悄地经过欢腾的小溪旁"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闪烁的繁星"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"掮着一夜的满足"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"钻进灰色的天幕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村潇潇洒洒的庭院里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"爆竹如迭出的妙语"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"和远天作亲切的交谈"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"与此起彼伏的鸡啼声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成一支激越雄壮的立体"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"交响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村那缕缕升腾的炊烟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弥漫着温馨的谷香"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"金鸡用翅膀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驮起一个喜气洋溢的新年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"温馨的春风"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把绿色纱衣轻轻扬起"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"洁白的栀子花"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驱逐着残冬的严寒"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿色的信念"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"注入村头封冻的柳枝"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"枝头的新芽绽开了笑口"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄鸡之声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"饱含着浓浓的情韵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把晨之门轻叩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"太阳如游鱼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"驾缤纷彩虹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在云海间跳跃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村热热闹闹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蓬蓬勃勃"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用烧酒渲染山峦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"酿造浓浓的希冀"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村被目光和激情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涂得鲜明透亮"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一条窄窄的小路"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"被巨大的步伐踩得宽宽"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"小孩争得脸红耳赤"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为飞向太阳的日期打赌"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄鸡报晓"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那嘹亮的歌喉"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"沉沉甸甸饱含激情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"涂抹山村风景线"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山村因歌声变得激动"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流水因歌声而永恒"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":4,"page_end":4}